text: Na tara allahane konala putra banavile ahe ani na tyacyasobata dusara koni upasya ahe, an'yatha pratyeka isvara apalya nirmitila ghe'una phirata rahila asata ani pratyekajana ekamekavara sresthatama honyaca prayatna karita rahila asata. Ji gunavaisitye he sangatata allaha tyapasuna pavitra ahe
